# Tests

- Run `.venv/bin/pytest` from the repo root (venv). Defaults include parallel workers (`-n auto`) and 100% branch coverage on `app/`; use `-n0` when debugging. See `docs/testing.md`.
- Monkeypatch `yfinance` in client tests; avoid live network in unit tests.
- Use `app.models.DataResult` where the client returns `DataResult`.
